<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Frontend Marketplace</title>

    <link rel="preconnect"
          href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">

    <link rel="preconnect"
          href="https://fonts.gstatic.com"
          crossorigin>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet">

    <style>

        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
            font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
        }

        body{

            min-height:100vh;

            display:flex;
            justify-content:center;
            align-items:center;

            overflow:hidden;

            background:
            linear-gradient(
            135deg,
            #0f172a,
            #1e293b,
            #312e81);

            position:relative;
        }

        /* Círculos decorativos */

        body::before{

            content:"";

            position:absolute;

            width:500px;
            height:500px;

            background:
            radial-gradient(
            circle,
            rgba(59,130,246,.5),
            transparent);

            top:-150px;
            left:-150px;

            animation:float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        body::after{

            content:"";

            position:absolute;

            width:500px;
            height:500px;

            background:
            radial-gradient(
            circle,
            rgba(168,85,247,.5),
            transparent);

            bottom:-150px;
            right:-150px;

            animation:float 10s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float{

            0%{
                transform:translateY(0);
            }

            50%{
                transform:translateY(30px);
            }

            100%{
                transform:translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .container{

            width:90%;
            max-width:900px;

            text-align:center;

            padding:60px;

            border-radius:30px;

            backdrop-filter:blur(25px);

            background:
            rgba(255,255,255,.08);

            border:
            1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);

            box-shadow:
            0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.4);

            z-index:2;
        }

        .badge{

            display:inline-block;

            padding:10px 20px;

            border-radius:999px;

            background:
            rgba(59,130,246,.15);

            color:#60a5fa;

            font-size:.9rem;

            margin-bottom:25px;
        }

        h1{

            color:white;

            font-size:4rem;

            font-weight:800;

            line-height:1.1;

            margin-bottom:20px;
        }

        .gradient{

            background:
            linear-gradient(
            90deg,
            #38bdf8,
            #818cf8,
            #c084fc);

            -webkit-background-clip:text;

            -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
        }

        p{

            color:#cbd5e1;

            font-size:1.2rem;

            max-width:700px;

            margin:auto;

            margin-bottom:40px;
        }

        .btn{

            display:inline-flex;

            align-items:center;
            justify-content:center;

            gap:10px;

            padding:18px 40px;

            text-decoration:none;

            color:white;

            font-size:1.1rem;
            font-weight:600;

            border-radius:15px;

            background:
            linear-gradient(
            135deg,
            #2563eb,
            #7c3aed);

            transition:.4s;

            box-shadow:
            0 10px 30px
            rgba(99,102,241,.4);
        }

        .btn:hover{

            transform:
            translateY(-5px)
            scale(1.05);

            box-shadow:
            0 20px 40px
            rgba(99,102,241,.6);
        }

        .cards{

            margin-top:60px;

            display:grid;

            grid-template-columns:
            repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));

            gap:20px;
        }

        .card{

            padding:25px;

            border-radius:20px;

            background:
            rgba(255,255,255,.05);

            border:
            1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);

            color:white;

            transition:.4s;
        }

        .card:hover{

            transform:
            translateY(-10px);

            background:
            rgba(255,255,255,.08);
        }

        .card h3{

            margin-bottom:10px;
        }

        .card p{

            font-size:.95rem;

            margin:0;

            color:#94a3b8;
        }

    </style>

</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="badge">
            🚀 Proyecto Marketplace Node.js + Express + MongoDB
        </div>

        <h1>

            Bienvenido a tu

            <span class="gradient">
                Frontend Marketplace
            </span>

        </h1>

        <p>

            Explora productos, consume APIs protegidas con API Key
            y visualiza información en tiempo real desde tu backend.

        </p>

        <a href="/api/v1/productos"
           class="btn">

            🛍 Ver Productos

        </a>

        <div class="cards">

            <div class="card">

                <h3>⚡ Axios</h3>

                <p>
                    Consumo eficiente de APIs REST.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h3>🔐 API Key</h3>

                <p>
                    Seguridad para proteger endpoints.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="card">

                <h3>🍃 MongoDB</h3>

                <p>
                    Base de datos NoSQL moderna.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>